41
00:03:26,720 --> 00:03:29,780
You are right. How about I tell Qiu Hua to go check?

42
00:03:29,780 --> 00:03:31,930
Don't do that!

43
00:03:31,930 --> 00:03:34,590
This Mei Manor is so daring.

44
00:03:34,590 --> 00:03:36,190
They dared to neglect me.

45
00:03:36,190 --> 00:03:38,520
