48
00:03:49,770 --> 00:03:50,920
Young Master!

49
00:03:50,920 --> 00:03:53,650
Young Master! It's time.

50
00:03:58,640 --> 00:04:01,250
Young Master! Young Master!

51
00:04:03,040 --> 00:04:05,510
His Lordship says that the princess has already arrived in Qingzhou.

52
00:04:05,510 --> 00:04:07,180
If you don't go to the entrance to welcome them,

53
00:04:07,180 --> 00:04:09,170
you'll face family discipline!

54
00:04:09,170 --> 00:04:11,000
- Welcome?
- Yes.

55
00:04:11,000 --> 00:04:12,410
- Family discipline?
- Yes.

56
00:04:21,010 --> 00:04:23,800
Lord, b-bad news!

57
00:04:23,800 --> 00:04:27,440
Don't be anxious. Speak slowly.

58
00:04:27,440 --> 00:04:29,800
The princess didn't come to the manor directly.

59
00:04:29,800 --> 00:04:31,740
Instead, she has checked into Ruyi Restaurant!

60
00:04:31,740 --> 00:04:33,140
- What?
- What?

61
00:04:33,140 --> 00:04:34,810
Th-This—

62
00:04:34,810 --> 00:04:37,660
Why is the princess staying at Ruyi Restaurant?

63
00:04:37,660 --> 00:04:40,020
Could it be because Shiqing didn't go to welcome her,

64
00:04:40,020 --> 00:04:41,730
so she's angry?

65
00:04:41,730 --> 00:04:43,710
Then hurry and tell Shiqing to go and welcome her!

66
00:04:43,710 --> 00:04:46,850
Third Young Master won't go no matter what.

67
00:04:46,850 --> 00:04:48,200
This unfilial son.

68
00:04:48,200 --> 00:04:50,690
My Lord, with Shiqing's current condition,

69
00:04:50,690 --> 00:04:52,900
I'm afraid it might not be convenient for him to go welcome her.

70
00:04:52,900 --> 00:04:56,500
Father, this won't do. If there's no other choice, I'll go.

71
00:04:56,500 --> 00:04:59,980
Quiet! Is the princess someone for you to go welcome?

72
00:04:59,980 --> 00:05:02,920
Tao Juzheng, hurry! Go there and welcome the princess.

73
00:05:02,920 --> 00:05:03,980
Me?

74
00:05:03,980 --> 00:05:06,340
- Go!
- Go!
- Yes.

75
00:05:07,270 --> 00:05:11,330
[Ruyi Restaurant]
- What's going on?
- How grand!

76
00:05:15,990 --> 00:05:18,660
My Lord, the princess came here very suddenly,

77
00:05:18,660 --> 00:05:20,210
