78
00:05:20,210 --> 00:05:23,820
If there are any difficulties, please forgive us.

79
00:05:23,820 --> 00:05:25,050
Is there anyone else here?

80
00:05:25,050 --> 00:05:30,120
Please don't worry. There is one guest left who is bathing and dressing. We'll ask her to leave soon.

81
00:05:30,120 --> 00:05:31,810
