84
00:05:36,770 --> 00:05:41,830
My Lady, are we lacking in courtesy by suddenly staying in an inn?

85
00:05:41,830 --> 00:05:43,450
Courtesy?

86
00:05:43,450 --> 00:05:45,190
I'm a relative of the imperial family,

87
00:05:45,190 --> 00:05:48,020
