88
00:05:48,020 --> 00:05:51,010
That Third Young Master Mei, on the other hand, didn't even come to receive us.

89
00:05:51,010 --> 00:05:53,820
He simply does not care about the imperial family.

90
00:05:53,820 --> 00:05:56,760
My Lady, about Third Young Master Mei not being able to come,

91
00:05:56,760 --> 00:05:59,150
