102
00:06:27,120 --> 00:06:30,720
- Everyone will die!
- That "bestowed" again!

103
00:06:30,720 --> 00:06:34,640
My Lady, please calm down. Here, have some more tea.

104
00:06:34,640 --> 00:06:38,410
- Stop talking. I want to be alone. Leave.
- All right, all right, all right.

105
00:06:38,410 --> 00:06:41,100
I'll leave. I'll leave.

106
00:06:41,100 --> 00:06:43,110
Think it over?

107
00:06:46,880 --> 00:06:49,190
Qiao Yun!

108
00:06:49,190 --> 00:06:51,820
