Who are you? Hasn't everyone been escorted out?

172
00:11:21,750 --> 00:11:25,170
- Lives are at stake. I'm trying to run for my life right now.
- What has happened?

173
00:11:25,170 --> 00:11:28,190
My father owes a gambling debt, so to repay it for him

174
00:11:28,190 --> 00:11:31,030
I have to go to the mountain fortress to be a bandit wife.

175
00:11:31,030 --> 00:11:34,540
The lives of girls nowadays are so difficult. Quickly go.

176
00:11:38,930 --> 00:11:42,360
I can't escape. If I run away, my father will lose his life.

177
00:11:42,360 --> 00:11:45,500
These people are simply despicable! I'll help you punish them.

178
00:11:45,500 --> 00:11:46,560
Who are you?

179
00:11:46,560 --> 00:11:49,610
Princess, the housekeeper is here!

180
00:11:53,990 --> 00:11:56,570
I ran into the wrong room.

181
00:11:56,570 --> 00:11:58,860
So this is the general's manor.

182
00:11:58,860 --> 00:12:01,180
