184
00:12:05,200 --> 00:12:09,450
The auspicious time has arrived! Begin the ceremony!

185
00:12:20,260 --> 00:12:23,420
First bow to Heaven and Earth.

186
00:12:32,260 --> 00:12:34,550
The princess is just nervous,

187
00:12:34,550 --> 00:12:37,300
so she forgot her etiquette.

188
00:12:37,300 --> 00:12:39,130
Princess.

189
00:12:41,300 --> 00:12:43,330
Bow.

190
00:12:46,480 --> 00:12:49,730
Second bow is to the parents.

191
00:12:51,850 --> 00:12:54,720
