193
00:13:02,950 --> 00:13:05,100
Bow.

194
00:13:08,960 --> 00:13:13,340
The ceremony has been completed! Enter the bridal chamber!

195
00:13:14,020 --> 00:13:16,660
Oh my god! I'm doomed now!

196
00:13:16,660 --> 00:13:18,660
What should I do?

197
