This is the Green Dragon Fort.

201
00:13:47,930 --> 00:13:49,870
I'm the godson of Nan Batian, the chief.

202
00:13:49,870 --> 00:13:52,590
I'm also the Third Boss here. Moreover, I'm your future husband.

203
00:13:52,590 --> 00:13:54,960
- Green Dragon Fort?
- Yes.

204
00:13:55,530 --> 00:13:57,490
- My husband?
- Yes.

205
00:14:00,030 --> 00:14:02,320
How could this be?

206
00:14:02,320 --> 00:14:04,660
Could it be that, earlier, I...

207
00:14:04,660 --> 00:14:07,920
[Lin Hai]

208
00:14:16,330 --> 00:14:20,330
I'll hide here. I'll drag it out for however long I can.

209
00:14:27,570 --> 00:14:29,420
[Lin Hai]

210
00:14:44,390 --> 00:14:46,270
Who are you?

211
00:14:48,660 --> 00:14:53,090
I... am your husband-to-be.

212
00:14:53,090 --> 00:14:56,690
My husband? Isn't he blind?

213
00:14:56,690 --> 00:15:00,100
If you dare come any closer, I'll call for someone! Guards!

214
00:15:03,420 --> 00:15:07,560
This bandit mistook me for that girl at the restaurant.

215
00:15:07,560 --> 00:15:09,130
What should I do?

216
00:15:09,130 --> 00:15:12,660
Should I tell him that he has the wrong person right now and I'm actually the princess?

217
00:15:12,660 --> 00:15:15,530
No, he might kill me.

218
00:15:15,530 --> 00:15:18,860
He might even do something worse to me.

219
00:15:18,860 --> 00:15:22,490
What are you thinking about? Let me tell you. Don't even think of running away.

220
00:15:22,490 --> 00:15:25,270
Your father has already pawned you off to me.

221
00:15:25,270 --> 00:15:27,960
It is natural to repay a debt.

222
00:15:27,960 --> 00:15:29,990
But don't worry. Being with me, Master Bao,

223
00:15:29,990 --> 00:15:33,040
I can guarantee that it will be a lot better than having to perform with your boulder-shattering chest.

224
00:15:33,630 --> 00:15:37,570
Right, M-Master Bao...

225
00:15:37,570 --> 00:15:41,560
Then, do you know what my name is? Do you know who I am?

226
00:15:43,260 --> 00:15:45,760
Aren't you Xiao Wanzi?

227
00:15:45,760 --> 00:15:49,970
Could it be that my martial arts skills were too advanced and you became muddle-headed from my blow?

228
00:15:49,970 --> 00:15:52,540
Xiao Wanzi?

229
00:15:52,540 --> 00:15:54,170
You must be hungry after a long day.

230
00:15:54,170 --> 00:15:57,360
I prepared a lot of delicious food. All of them are my favorites.

231
00:15:59,600 --> 00:16:01,580
Wow!

232
00:16:03,590 --> 00:16:07,400
What are you doing? Why are you just staying over there? The dishes are going to get cold.

233
00:16:09,900 --> 00:16:11,960
Why are you just staying here?

234
00:16:11,960 --> 00:16:14,060
Then come over by yourself.

235
00:16:19,130 --> 00:16:22,640
Look! They're all delicious. Come on, hurry up and eat.

236
00:16:22,640 --> 00:16:26,330
You haven't seen such delicious food while you were performing on the streets, right?

237
00:16:26,330 --> 00:16:29,170
Look at how thin you are. You must be starving.

238
00:16:29,170 --> 00:16:34,280
Don't worry. Being with me, you won't ever be hungry.

239
00:16:34,280 --> 00:16:37,030
I'll raise you to be chubby.
(like raising farm animals)

240
00:16:45,620 --> 00:16:49,550
I want to go home! I want to see my father!

241
00:16:49,550 --> 00:16:53,020
Why are you crying? Do these not suit your taste?

242
00:16:53,020 --> 00:16:56,000
There's also this! Here, eat a chicken.

243
00:16:59,430 --> 00:17:02,650
Enough. Stop crying. Let's do this.

244
00:17:02,650 --> 00:17:05,870
Except for sending you home, I'll promise you anything else you want.

245
00:17:05,870 --> 00:17:10,510
T-Then, can you promise to not touch me?

246
00:17:10,510 --> 00:17:14,430
Never touch you? How is that possible? Why did I marry you then?

247
00:17:14,430 --> 00:17:20,050
My godfather said to marry you so you can give me heirs.

248
00:17:21,770 --> 00:17:23,550
Master Bao!

249
00:17:23,550 --> 00:17:28,500
- Master Bao.
- Yes?
- The big boss said to bring your new bride to see him.

250
00:17:28,500 --> 00:17:31,540
- All right, I got it. You may go.
- All right.

