00:17:59,200 --> 00:18:02,200
If you take it off, I'm done for!

254
00:18:02,200 --> 00:18:05,000
If I say they got the wrong person, someone will believe me. Right?

255
00:18:05,000 --> 00:18:06,800
What should I do if they don't believe me?

256
00:18:07,590 --> 00:18:10,630
What should I do if I get captured and beheaded?

257
00:18:13,200 --> 00:18:14,400
What are you doing?

258
00:18:14,400 --> 00:18:19,200
What? Princess, are you looking down on me, a blind man?

259
00:18:30,500 --> 00:18:35,700
Is he really blind? Was he already blind when I saw him in the carriage last time?

260
00:18:39,000 --> 00:18:40,400
What are you doing? What are you doing?

261
00:18:40,400 --> 00:18:44,300
I-I'm telling you, this is a misunderstanding!

262
00:18:44,300 --> 00:18:45,600
I... I didn't want to marry anyone.

263
00:18:45,600 --> 00:18:46,600
You didn't want to marry?

264
00:18:46,600 --> 00:18:48,200
I was forced!

265
00:18:48,200 --> 00:18:49,200
No, no.

266
00:18:49,200 --> 00:18:53,400
I-I don't know how I was escorted here to the Mei Manor.

267
00:18:53,400 --> 00:18:57,000
This is a marriage that was imperially bestowed. No one can get out of it.

268
00:18:57,000 --> 00:19:00,400
Since neither of us wanted to marry, then let us steer clear of each other.

269
00:19:00,400 --> 00:19:02,200
We'll each stay in our own places.

270
00:19:02,200 --> 00:19:06,400
Wait! We're already at this stage, how do we stay in our own places?

271
00:19:06,400 --> 00:19:11,800
We are married in name, but we certainly will not consummate it.

272
00:19:11,800 --> 00:19:14,400
That means you won't touch me?

273
00:19:14,400 --> 00:19:18,800
What? Princess, do you want to really be married to me now?

274
00:19:18,800 --> 00:19:21,000
No, no, no! I agree, I agree!

275
00:19:21,000 --> 00:19:23,400
- I agree! I agree!
- Excellent!

276
00:19:26,500 --> 00:19:28,900
I've never seen such a narcissist.

277
00:19:41,400 --> 00:19:44,600
Once I'm full and energetic tomorrow, I'll run away!

278
00:19:45,400 --> 00:19:47,000
That's not right.

279
00:19:47,000 --> 00:19:51,400
Isn't he blind? I can leave right now.

280
00:20:04,100 --> 00:20:07,200
What? Do you want to run away?

281
00:20:09,000 --> 00:20:12,200
You ate too much. No matter how quietly you walk, I can still hear you clearly.

282
00:20:12,200 --> 00:20:15,200
Besides, tonight is our wedding night.

283
00:20:15,200 --> 00:20:19,000
It's not safe for the bride to run around everywhere.

284
00:20:19,000 --> 00:20:22,700
Our Mei Manor guards are very strict.

285
00:20:43,900 --> 00:20:47,200
What are you doing? Wait! Wait! What are you doing?

286
00:20:47,200 --> 00:20:48,400
Going to sleep.

287
00:20:48,400 --> 00:20:50,100
If you're sleeping on the bed, where am I sleeping?

288
00:20:50,100 --> 00:20:52,200
If you want to sleep on the bed too, I don't mind.

289
00:20:52,200 --> 00:20:53,600
I mind!

290
00:20:53,600 --> 00:20:55,300
I...

291
00:20:55,300 --> 00:20:59,100
I"m a princess. I am beautiful and noble.

292
00:20:59,100 --> 00:21:01,000
How can you take advantage?

293
00:21:01,000 --> 00:21:02,600
Then do as you like.

294
00:21:02,600 --> 00:21:04,200
Do as I like?

295
00:21:04,200 --> 00:21:05,800
Is that something a person should say?

296
00:21:05,800 --> 00:21:07,400
You are a man,

297
00:21:07,400 --> 00:21:11,000
so aren't you ashamed to take the entire bed?

298
00:21:11,000 --> 00:21:12,600
This is my bed.

299
00:21:12,600 --> 00:21:16,500
By the way, your blankets are over there. Go get them yourself.

300
00:21:18,600 --> 00:21:20,600
Fine.

301
00:21:20,600 --> 00:21:22,400
Seeing that you are...

302
00:21:22,400 --> 00:21:25,000
a blind man,

303
00:21:25,000 --> 00:21:27,400
I won't fuss about this with you.

304
00:21:27,400 --> 00:21:31,200
I'm considerate. I can sleep anywhere.

305
00:21:35,800 --> 00:21:37,400
This is bad.

306
00:21:42,440 --> 00:21:44,930
Godfather, we're here.

307
00:21:45,600 --> 00:21:48,400
Xiao Bao, look at you.

308
00:21:48,400 --> 00:21:54,000
You two haven't even gotten married yet and you carried her back here like an anxious monkey.

309
00:21:54,000 --> 00:21:58,500
I was anxious and wanted to see what my wife looked like.

310
00:21:58,500 --> 00:22:00,000
Are you satisfied?

311
00:22:00,000 --> 00:22:04,200
Godfather, I am so satisfied. This is all thanks to Master Wu.

312
00:22:05,350 --> 00:22:07,410
S-Satisfied?

313
00:22:09,700 --> 00:22:11,500
Bride.

314
00:22:11,500 --> 00:22:14,400
Lift up your head up. Let me take a look.

315
00:22:14,400 --> 00:22:18,000
Wanzi, lift up your head up. Godfather wants to see you.

316
00:22:18,810 --> 00:22:20,480
Hurry.

317
00:22:34,000 --> 00:22:35,200
Godfather?

318
00:22:35,200 --> 00:22:36,600
Chief?

319
00:22:37,800 --> 00:22:39,200
Godfather?

320
00:22:39,200 --> 00:22:40,600
Chief?

321
00:22:42,200 --> 00:22:44,000
Beautiful.

322
00:22:45,500 --> 00:22:48,300
This girl is beautiful.

323
00:22:55,140 --> 00:22:56,590
Miss.

324
00:22:57,610 --> 00:23:00,580
You were carried up the mountain by this lad just like this?

325
00:23:01,400 --> 00:23:03,600
He didn't scare you, did he?

326
00:23:03,600 --> 00:23:05,800
I was scared.

327
00:23:05,800 --> 00:23:09,300
He doesn't know how to be tender toward women at all.

328
00:23:09,300 --> 00:23:10,800
Godfather.

329
00:23:10,800 --> 00:23:12,800
We already made up earlier.

330
00:23:12,800 --> 00:23:14,000
Who made up with you?

331
00:23:14,000 --> 00:23:16,800
Save me some face in front of Godfather.

332
00:23:16,800 --> 00:23:18,400
- Xiao Bao.
- Yes?

333
00:23:19,400 --> 00:23:23,300
You are so fortunate.

334
00:23:23,300 --> 00:23:26,400
It's you, Godfather, who picked well.

335
00:23:28,570 --> 00:23:30,710
Get up!

336
00:23:38,700 --> 00:23:40,200
Is it this girl?

337
00:23:40,200 --> 00:23:42,000
Why didn't you get my approval first to get married!

338
00:23:42,000 --> 00:23:45,200
If I'm getting married, why should I tell you? Why do I need your approval?

339
00:23:45,200 --> 00:23:46,800
I—

340
00:23:46,800 --> 00:23:48,300
- Father!
- Yes?

341
00:23:52,600 --> 00:23:55,600
You are marrying this woman, right?

342
00:23:55,600 --> 00:23:57,800
If you marry her, don't even think about having peaceful days!

343
00:23:57,800 --> 00:24:00,400
- What does it have to do with you?
- I—

344
00:24:00,400 --> 00:24:02,700
This violent temper of mine...

345
00:24:02,700 --> 00:24:04,800
Xiao Bao!

346
00:24:04,800 --> 00:24:07,900
Hurry and go! Go!

347
00:24:07,900 --> 00:24:10,600
- Let's go!
- Nan Xiang!
- Father!

348
00:24:10,600 --> 00:24:12,800
Why are you doing this?

349
00:24:12,800 --> 00:24:14,000
I—

350
00:24:14,000 --> 00:24:17,200
What is so great about Xiao Bao? He's heartless, isn't he?

351
00:24:17,200 --> 00:24:20,900
Father, he is great! I like him!

352
00:24:20,900 --> 00:24:22,600
Are you my father or not?

353
00:24:22,600 --> 00:24:27,800
Xiao Bao is about to get married! Are you my father or not?

354
00:24:27,800 --> 00:24:29,400
I promise you!

355
00:24:29,400 --> 00:24:32,400
I will definitely teach that heartless Xiao Bao a lesson for you. All right?

356
00:24:32,400 --> 00:24:33,800
No!

357
00:24:33,800 --> 00:24:37,200
What use is that? Even if you teach him a lesson, isn't he still going to get married?

358
00:24:37,200 --> 00:24:39,800
- Father!
- Fine!

359
00:24:39,800 --> 00:24:43,400
I promise you. I will give you a satisfactory answer, all right?

360
00:24:43,400 --> 00:24:46,400
Go back first, all right? I have something to discuss with Old Wu.

361
00:24:46,400 --> 00:24:49,800
- Are you sure?
- I'm sure. Hurry and go back.

362
00:24:53,100 --> 00:24:54,600
- Old Wu.
- Yes?

363
00:24:54,600 --> 00:24:55,700
Come.

364
00:24:55,700 --> 00:24:57,200
What is it, Chief?

365
00:25:02,000 --> 00:25:05,200
You unreliable wicked thing.

366
00:25:05,200 --> 00:25:10,500
You even told me about her boulder-shattering chest and then she's like this.

367
00:25:10,500 --> 00:25:16,000
Why don't I see you finding me such a beautiful bandit wife like her?

368
00:25:16,000 --> 00:25:17,000
Chief.

369
00:25:17,000 --> 00:25:20,800
This is my first time seeing her, too. Who knew she would look all right?

370
00:25:20,800 --> 00:25:23,700
Still talking?

371
00:25:29,450 --> 00:25:31,000
Damn!

372
00:25:32,640 --> 00:25:34,460
Here, have a seat.

373
00:25:35,300 --> 00:25:37,900
Enough. Stop wearing such a long face.

374
00:25:37,900 --> 00:25:39,600
Don't worry.

375
00:25:39,600 --> 00:25:43,270
Nan Xiang has no bad intentions. In the future, when you get used to her, it'll be all right.

376
00:25:44,080 --> 00:25:46,790
Who has a future with you?

377
00:25:49,960 --> 00:25:53,270
Now that I'm full, I'm actually a bit tired.

378
00:25:53,270 --> 00:25:56,380
Wife, let's go to sleep. Come on.

379
00:25:56,380 --> 00:25:59,510
Hold on! Who are you calling "wife"?

380
00:26:03,100 --> 00:26:04,880
I'm exhausted.

381
00:26:04,880 --> 00:26:07,650
Wh-What are you doing?

382
00:26:07,650 --> 00:26:09,250
Taking my shoes off to go to bed.

383
00:26:09,250 --> 00:26:12,270
Wait! If you're sleeping here, then where do I sleep?

384
00:26:13,120 --> 00:26:16,650
Do you want to sleep on the left or right side? You can choose.

385
00:26:16,650 --> 00:26:19,600
Are you a scoundrel? Get out immediately!

386
00:26:19,600 --> 00:26:20,850
Then, where do I sleep?

387
00:26:20,850 --> 00:26:23,500
Sleep wherever you like. If you don't get out,

388
00:26:23,500 --> 00:26:25,840
- I'll die in front of you.
- Don't!

389
00:26:26,840 --> 00:26:29,550
Fine, fine, fine! I'll leave.

390
00:26:29,550 --> 00:26:32,450
- I'll leave, all right?
- I'm dead.

391
00:26:44,250 --> 00:26:46,210
Master Bao.

392
00:26:46,210 --> 00:26:48,500
How come you aren't going in the bridal chamber tonight?

393
00:26:48,500 --> 00:26:50,790
One hour on a spring night is worth a thousand pieces of gold.
(A romantic night is priceless.)

394
00:26:50,790 --> 00:26:52,630
A thousand pieces of gold, my butt!

395
00:26:52,630 --> 00:26:54,550
Although we are bandits,

396
00:26:54,550 --> 00:26:56,240
we still have to be cultured.

397
00:26:56,240 --> 00:26:59,740
How could we consummate it when we're not yet married?

398
00:26:59,740 --> 00:27:02,070
Also, go snatch some things that women use tomorrow.

399
00:27:02,070 --> 00:27:05,740
Things like lipstick, powder, and blush. Got it?

400
00:27:05,740 --> 00:27:08,350
Stay here and keep watch. If you don't, then you'll be responsible.

401
00:27:08,350 --> 00:27:10,060
Yes.

402
00:27:14,070 --> 00:27:16,460
I have to hurry and think of a way to escape.

403
00:27:16,460 --> 00:27:18,830
It seems Master Xiao Bao actually likes me.

404
00:27:18,830 --> 00:27:22,540
Perhaps I can use him to escape.

405
00:27:42,930 --> 00:27:44,810
No.

406
00:28:50,650 --> 00:28:52,930
Young Master, I apologize for the wait.

407
00:28:53,620 --> 00:28:55,210
What have you found?

408
00:28:55,210 --> 00:28:58,390
A few days ago, a lunatic appeared on the streets of Qingzhou.

409
00:28:58,390 --> 00:29:01,620
While he was spewing nonsense, he mentioned the murder of Madam Mei.

410
00:29:01,620 --> 00:29:03,710
I ordered my men to tie him up.

411
00:29:03,710 --> 00:29:04,890
What is his background?

412
00:29:04,890 --> 00:29:07,000
He is Crazy Old Chen from Qingzhou.

413
00:29:07,000 --> 00:29:09,680
He has a crazy personality and does all kinds of evil.

414
00:29:09,680 --> 00:29:11,700
Ten years ago, he disappeared from here.

415
00:29:11,700 --> 00:29:13,420
Recently, he's wandered back to Qingzhou.

416
00:29:13,420 --> 00:29:16,280
He's gone completely insane now.

417
00:29:16,280 --> 00:29:18,570
He has no family, no friends.

418
00:29:18,570 --> 00:29:20,300
He usually survives only by begging.

419
00:29:20,300 --> 00:29:21,610
What else did you find out?

420
00:29:21,610 --> 00:29:23,710
He mentioned Omniscient Old Lai of the Beggars Gang.

421
00:29:23,710 --> 00:29:25,830
He specializes in finding people and building connections.

422
00:29:25,830 --> 00:29:28,240
I found out that the year Madam was killed,

423
00:29:28,240 --> 00:29:31,080
he was looking for an assassin among the criminal sect.

424
00:29:31,080 --> 00:29:32,390
Where is he now?

425
00:29:32,390 --> 00:29:36,110
It is said he will appear at the shack next to the Temple of the Land Deity.

426
00:29:36,110 --> 00:29:37,850
I've already sent someone to keep an eye out.

427
00:29:37,850 --> 00:29:40,400
You must bring him to me alive.

428
00:29:40,400 --> 00:29:41,740
Yes.

429
00:30:35,330 --> 00:30:37,230
All right.

430
00:30:40,080 --> 00:30:42,900
Night-Spirited Hero.

431
00:30:45,100 --> 00:30:48,700
Let's uphold justice together.

432
00:30:48,700 --> 00:30:51,470
...together.

